{"type":"message","id":"d427b56c","parentId":"38a8c7d3","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:30:06.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the company organization structure information from what I've gathered. The organizational structure details were mentioned in the company profile page content. Let me recall and verify this information.\n\nFrom the data I collected earlier, the organizational structure mentions:\n- 总部下设十个职能部门、一座直属矿山和一个项目部\n- Five subsidiaries and one participating commercial bank\n\n\n- Now I need to search through my previous responses more carefully to find the specific details about these entities and their relationships within the organization.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**四川里伍铜业组织结构：**\n\n### 总部架构\n- **十个职能部门**（具体名称未在网页公开页面列出）\n- **一座直属矿山**（主体为里伍铜矿）\n- **一个项目部**（中咀铜矿开发项目部）\n\n### 子公司体系（5家子公司 + 1家参股商业银行）\n\n| 公司名称 | 性质/备注 |\n|----------|-----------|\n| **雅砻江矿业公司** | 控股子公司，被评为\"四川省健康企业\"；2011年成立，运营黑牛洞铜矿 |\n| **里铜电力有限责任公司** | 2007年成立，运营三垭河梯级电站（全部并网发电） |\n| **金伯利地勘公司** | 原四川金伯利地质勘查有限公司，2009年全资收购 |\n| **丹巴协作铂镍公司** | 2008年联合收购 |\n\n以及一家**参股商业银行**。\n\n### 总部选址\n- **注册地址/办公总部：** 四川省康定市炉城镇向阳街137号\n- **第二办公区：** 成都\n\n---\n\n*注：十个职能部门的具体名称在网页上没有详细列出，如果需要可以进入\"组织结构\"页面查看完整信息。*"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":34890,"output":473,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35363,"cost":{"input":0.06978,"output":0.0056760000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.075456}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776878995273,"responseId":"chatcmpl-uaa2xtcj8iwqd9of3gkh"}}
