{"type":"message","id":"cce1850d","parentId":"e5a25c87","timestamp":"2026-04-22T17:50:56.719Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-23 01:50 GMT+8] graph TD\n subgraph 四川里伍铜业股份有限公司\n direction TB\n\n A[四川里伍铜业股份有限公司]:::company --> B[党委]:::governance;\n A --> C[董事会]:::governance;\n A --> D[监事会]:::governance;\n\n subgraph 总经理层\n E[总经理层]:::management --> F[综合管理部]:::department;\n E --> G[人力资源部]:::department;\n E --> H[财务部]:::department;\n E --> I[投资部]:::department;\n E --> J[资源勘查部(科技部)]:::department;\n E --> K[生产运营部]:::department;\n E --> L[安全环保部]:::department;\n E --> M[市场营销部]:::department;\n E --> N[设备物资部]:::department;\n E --> O[审计监察部]:::department;\n\n E --> P[直属矿山]:::business_unit;\n E --> Q[中咀铜矿项目部]:::business_unit;\n\n E --> R[雅砻江矿业公司]:::subsidiary;\n E --> S[里铜电力公司]:::subsidiary;\n E --> T[金伯利地勘公司]:::subsidiary;\n E --> U[丹巴协作铂镍公司]:::subsidiary;\n E --> V[杨柳坪矿业公司]:::subsidiary;\n E --> W[参股商业银行]:::subsidiary;\n end\n\n B ~~~ C;\n C ~~~ D;\n D --> E;\n end\n\n classDef company fill:#2E8B57,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,font-weight:bold;\n classDef governance fill:#4682B4,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;\n classDef management fill:#FFA500,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;\n classDef department fill:#F0F0F0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;\n classDef business_unit fill:#E6E6FA,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;\n classDef subsidiary fill:#FFFACD,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;\n\n style A text-align:center;\n style B text-align:center;\n style C text-align:center;\n style D text-align:center;\n style E text-align:center;\n这是组织架结构图，记好。"}],"timestamp":1776880256716}}
